Woody Johnson, Jonathan Tisch Named Chairmen of Super Bowl Host Committee

-- B y   E b e n   N o v y - W i l l i a m s
-- 
2011-09-27T13:18:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-27/woody-johnson-jonathan-tisch-named-chairmen-of-super-bowl-host-committee.html
New York Jets owner  Woody Johnson 
and New York Giants treasurer Jonathan Tisch were named co-
chairmen of the 2014 Super Bowl Host Committee.  National Football League owners voted last year to award
the championship game of the most-watched U.S. television sport
to MetLife Stadium in  East Rutherford ,  New Jersey , home of the
Giants and Jets.  The appointments were made by Alfred F. Kelly Jr., chief
executive officer of the committee.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jay Beberman at 
 jbeberman@bloomberg.net  